---
import PortalShell from "../layouts/PortalShell.astro";
---

<PortalShell activePage="topics" title="专题" description="从不同主题进入阿臭弟的小站内容。">
  <header class="page-hero portal-container">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span></span> Topics</p>
    <div class="page-hero-row"><div><h1>专题导航</h1><p>后续会按电商 AI 场景，把文章和资源整理成更清晰的专题入口。</p></div></div>
  </header>
  <section class="portal-section topic-section">
    <div class="portal-container topic-grid">
      <a class="topic-card topic-reading" href="/articles/"><span>01</span><i data-lucide="image"></i><h2>AI 生图</h2><p>电商主图、详情图、场景图和素材生产相关内容。</p><em>进入文章 <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></em></a>
      <a class="topic-card topic-engineering" href="/articles/"><span>02</span><i data-lucide="video"></i><h2>AI 生视频</h2><p>商品视频、短视频素材和视频脚本相关实战整理。</p><em>进入文章 <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></em></a>
      <a class="topic-card topic-product" href="/market/"><span>03</span><i data-lucide="sparkles"></i><h2>商业实战Skill</h2><p>面向不同电商场景的 Skill 框架和知识库入口。</p><em>进入AI实战库 <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></em></a>
      <a class="topic-card topic-notes" href="/tools/"><span>04</span><i data-lucide="wrench"></i><h2>资源工具</h2><p>日常创作、运营和 AI 工作流里会用到的工具资源。</p><em>进入资源工具 <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></em></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PortalShell>
